          "notes": "GLM-5 Mid-train: concatenating repo-level code files, commit diffs, GitHub issues, pull requests, and relevant source files into unified training sequences (10 million issue–PR pairs, 160B unique tokens)\n\nGLM-5 SFT: A large number of execution environments, with particular emphasis on real-world scenarios and long-horizon tasks. We further improve the SFT data using **expert reinforcement learning and rejection sampling**. Erroneous segments within trajectories are retained but **masked out** in the loss function, allowing the model to learn error correction behaviors without reinforcing incorrect actions.",
